tune.name: My Clarinet is Back!
tune.author: Nicolas “Niols” Jeannerod
tune.content:
\relative f' <<
  \new Voice {
    \clef treble
    \time 6/8
    \key b \minor

    \repeat volta 2 {
      \partial 4 r8 fis |
      b4 fis8 b4 fis8 |
      d'8 cis b cis b a |
      b4 fis8 b4 fis8 |
      d'8 cis b cis4 fis,8 |
      \break

      b4 fis8 b4 fis8 |
      d'8 cis b cis b a |
      g8 fis e fis4 cis'8 |
      b4. b8
    } \break

    \repeat volta 2 {
      d8 e |
      fis4 d8 d cis d |
      fis4 d8 d cis d |
      g8 fis e fis e d |
      cis4. cis8 d e |
      \break

      fis4 d8 d cis d |
      fis4 d8 d cis d |
      cis8 b a fis4 cis'8 |
      b4. b8
    }
  }

  \new ChordNames {
    \chordmode {
      s4 |
      b2.:m | b4.:m a | b2.:m | b4.:m a |
      b2.:m | b4.:m a | g fis:7 | b2.:m |

      d2. | d2. | g4. d | a2.:7 |
      d2. | d2. | a4. fis:7 | b4.:m
    }
  }
>>
